SUMMARY:The Occult Influence of Music
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n-Free Admission - Refres
 hments - Open to the public -\n\n**The Occult Influence of Music**\nwritte
 n by Elmira H. Zeller\, S.R.C.\n\nThe vibrations created by music can rais
 e our consciousness from one state into a higher one. This is the hidden o
 r "occult" influence of music. In this fascinating presentation we learn h
 ow music vibrations create subtle overtones that can evoke emotions and tr
 ansport one into the realm of memory and inspiration.\n\nPresented by: Dan
  Villalva\, Pronaos Archivist\n\nAbout the Santa Rosa Pronaos\nWe hold a m
 onthly public presentation on mystical or metaphysical topics as a public 
 service. The topics and speakers vary and no previous knowledge or experie
 nce is required. Just bring an open mind and heart.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pron
 aos doesn't charge for admission. We operate under the law of AMRA. You ma
 y give as your heart and mind direct you.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos is a 5
 01c3 Educational Non=profit\, an affiliated body of the Rosicrucian Englis
 h Grand Lodge for the Americas and the Caribbean.
