SUMMARY:The Oracles of Delphi – Seeing Beyond the Answer
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**The Oracles of Delphi 
 - Seeing Beyond the Answer**\n\nIn this presentation\, Grand Master Julie 
 Scott will introduce us to the ancient Oracles of Delphi\, not as predicto
 rs of the future\, but as catalysts for expanded perception. Drawing on hi
 storical accounts of the Oracles and the symbolic nature of their propheci
 es\, we can see how ambiguity was used to deepen awareness rather than pro
 vide certainty. We will reconsider our own relationship to answers\, insig
 ht\, and interpretation. Through story\, philosophy\, and a brief meditati
 ve experience\, we will experience a shift from seeking clarity to cultiva
 ting deeper seeing. Ultimately\, this suggests that the true oracle is not
  external – but emerges in how we perceive and make meaning.\n\n**Please
  RSVP to access log-in link. Click Attend Online button below.**
