SUMMARY:The Color Organs of the Master of the Rose Cross
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**The Color Organs of th
 e Master of the Rose Cross**\n\nA key teaching tool of the Rosicrucian wee
 kly studies and exercises is the Cosmic Keyboard\, an exemplification of t
 he great interconnecting octaves of vibration within us and throughout the
  Cosmos. A remarkable demonstration of these resonant relationships and sy
 mpathetic correspondences are the color organs designed and created by Pas
 t Imperator H. Spencer Lewis. We will consider their inspiration\, constru
 ction\, and demonstration of Rosicrucian laws and principles. Join Hugh Mc
 Cague on this adventure in history realized anew today for our Self-Master
 y\, harmonious living\, and service.\n\n**Please RSVP to access log-in lin
 k. Click Attend Online button below.**
