SUMMARY:Experiencing and Emulating the Cosmic III
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**Experiencing and Emula
 ting the Cosmic III**\n\nPast Imperator of the Rosicrucian Order\, AMORC\,
  Ralph M. Lewis in his book *The Sanctuary of Self* points out to us that 
 the Cosmic is the object and the world is the image. For our full maturati
 on\, we need to both experience the magnificence of the Cosmic and then em
 ulate that experience in our lives\, service\, personal contacts\, and env
 ironment. Join Hugh McCague as we continue to explore how this dual proces
 s is a key to understanding life\, Self-Mastery\, and why mysticism is so 
 practical.\n\n**Please RSVP to access log-in link. Click Attend Online but
 ton below.**
